name: Jorney To The Past.4 (Control)
description:
My body is like vehicle that I can control through my emotions and thoughts. Knowing when to move forward, also when to stop at the right time. The journey of life is an interesting part of human life. So let me understand many things through photography.

Tubuhku adalah Kendaraan yang kukendalikan melalui emosi dan pikiran. Kapan kita harus berani maju, kapan kita berhenti pada waktu yang tepat. Perjalanan hidup menjadi bagian menarik dalam hidup manusia. Maka ijinkan aku mengenal banyak hal melalui fotografi.
